description: Upsales is a Swedish-founded software-as-a-service company providing an AI-driven, end-to-end sales and marketing platform. It is designed for sales-driven B2B companies—typically ranging from 50 to 1,000 employees—to manage CRM, marketing automation, business intelligence, and billing.
